1. *Užasno* je vruće danas. (It's terribly hot today.)
2. Ova situacija je *užasna*. (This situation is horrible.)
3. Nisam mogao da gledam taj film, bio je *užasan*. (I couldn't watch that movie, it was terrible.)
4. *Užasno* mi nedostaješ. (I terribly miss you.)
5. Kada sam video šta se desilo, osetio sam *užas* u grudima. (When I saw what happened, I felt horror in my chest.)
6. Moramo da popravimo ovaj *užasan* problem. (We need to fix this terrible problem.)
7. *Užasno* sam umoran. (I'm terribly tired.)
8. Ovo je bila *užasna* greška. (This was a terrible mistake.)
9. Ovaj grad je *užasan* za vožnju. (This city is terrible for driving.)
10. Osećam *užasnu* glad. (I feel a terrible hunger.)